---
name: Step-by-step collaboration preferred
description: User prefers working through tasks incrementally rather than having Claude generate full automation scripts
type: feedback
---

When building new infrastructure or workflows, work through it one step at a time with the user rather than generating a complete script upfront.

**Why:** User explicitly chose incremental approach ("let's take it a step at a time") when offered a full replacement script for historical evaluation.

**How to apply:** Propose the next concrete step, execute it, verify, then move on. Don't batch everything into a single script unless asked.
